<template>
    <v-dialog v-model="dialogVisible" persistent max-width="370">
      <v-card>
        <v-card-title class="headline"></v-card-title>
        <v-card-text>{{descricao}}</v-card-text>
        <v-card-actions>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn color="secondary" text @click="dashboard()">OK</v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
      </v-card>
    </v-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    mounted(){
        document.addEventListener("keyup", this.onKeyPress)
        },

    destroyed() {
        document.removeEventListener("keyup", this.onKeyPress)
  },
  
  methods:{
      dashboard() {
                this.$router.push(this.urlRedirecionamento + this.id)
                this.toogleVisible()
            },
      onKeyPress(e){
        if(this.dialogVisible){
            if(e.key.toLowerCase() === "enter") {
              this.dashboard();
            }
      }
    },
  },

  name: 'dialog-agradecimento',
  props:{
    dialogVisible: Boolean,
    toogleVisible: Function,
    descricao: String,
    id: Number,
    urlRedirecionamento: String
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
